Easy to install and works on Win7SP1/64bit(Without compatibility mode), using common computer sense.  Three times: Setup then find patch(WarChiefs patch is hidden a bit compared to the others).  Then copy and replace the game executables with those that don't have CD checks.

The only error is the packaging and the readme.  For some reason an unneeded ISO is included and multiple cracked EXEs of each version are included.  Daemon tools is not needed and there is no need to mount anything.  Also Win7/64bit users need not copy the IPHLPAPI.DLL to begin with in the one crack folder.
